-- Terminal Triage: Level 03 — Student Tech Hub
-- Focus: high volume, software issues, introduce customer support lab (psychiatry).
%Name = "Student Tech Hub"
%MapFile = "tt_level_03.map"

%LevelBriefingTable.en = "University campuses are a goldmine for tech repair shops — and a nightmare to manage.You're dealing with spilled-coffee laptops, ransomwear infections, overheating gaming rigs, and Wi-Fi configuration nightmares. Volume is relentless and budgets are tight.Expand your diagnostic lab, open a Customer Support wing for user-error cases, and keep devices flowing through your workshop.Earn a reputation of at least 700, accumulate $100,000 in the bank, and fix at least 200 devices to prove you can handle the load."

%LevelDebriefingTable.en = "Excellent throughput! You kept the student queue moving and earned some serious brand trust.The corporate sector is watching. Brace yourself for the next assignment."

